devdoc.author: Watson Bosquet
devdoc.details: This contract is used as a proxy contract. Each user is created via UserFactory. It can received token

params._adminAddress: Address to grant Emits a AdminAdded event

params._arena: Name of the arena of the fight
params._fightType: Type of fight, championship match or a regular fight night
params._fileCID: IPFS CID for the NFT metadata Emits a FightCreated event
params._fileLink: Link of the picture advertising the fight
params._location: Name of the location of the fight

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params.metadataCID: IPFS CID for the NFT's metadata Emits a transfer event

returns._0: the appropriate uri for the token

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params._userAddress: Address of the user added as a participant Emits a UserHasJoinedAFight event

devdoc.title: Fight

safeMint(uint256,address,string).notice: Mint an NFT that represents the event. The owner is the Fight contract until there is a winner

userJoinAFightAsJudgeEnthusiast(uint256,.notice: Add user as a judge to a fight

withdraw().notice: Send all the money of the contract to the super admin wallet Emits Withdrawal event
